Installation:
1. Install logwatch, sysstat (try 'aptitude install logwatch sysstat' on Debian/Ubuntu
2. Install the File::Which CPAN Module: 
2.1 perl -MCPAN -e 'install File::Which' 
3. Copy sysstat-selfnet.conf to /etc/logwatch/conf/services
4. Copy sysstat-selfnet to /etc/logwatch/scripts/services 
5. Put 'Service = sysstat-selfnet' into your /etc/logwatch/logwatch.conf

Have fun! :-) 

